
'''''The Constant Gardener''''' ni filim iri ituruka muri England and German yasohotse muri 2005 iyoborwa na  Fernando Meirelles <ref>https://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=56739.html</ref>. Amashusho yakozwe na Jeffrey Caine ashingiye ku gitabo cya John le Carré cyo mu 2001 cyitwa The Constant Gardener <ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-constant-gardener-2005</ref>. Iyi nkuru ikurikira Justin Quayle ( Ralph Fiennes ), umudipolomate w’Ubwongereza muri Kenya<ref>https://www.spiritualityandpractice.com/films/reviews/view/9969/the-constant-gardener</ref>, ubwo yageragezaga gukemura ikibazo cy’iyicwa ry’umugore we Tessa ( Rachel Weisz ), uharanira Amnesty, asimburana n’ibintu byinshi byerekana amateka y’urukundo rwabo<ref>https://www.spiritualityandpractice.com/films/reviews/view/9969/the-constant-gardener</ref>.

Iyi filime yafatiwe amashusho ahitwa Loiyangalani no mucyaro cya Kibera, igice cya [[Nairobi]], muri [[Kenya]]<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2005/nov/11/3</ref> . Ibintu muri kariya gace byagize ingaruka ku bakinnyi ndetse no ku bakozi ku buryo bashizeho Constant Gardener Trust kugira ngo batange uburezi bw'ibanze kuri iyo midugudu<ref>https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2005/nov/11/3</ref>. Uyu mugambi washingiye ku buryo budasobanutse ku rubanza rwabayeho i Kano, muri Nijeriya<ref>https://www.focusfeatures.com/the_constant_gardener</ref> . Impapuro za DVD zasohotse muri Amerika ku ya 1 Mutarama 2006 no mu Bwongereza ku ya 13 Werurwe 2006<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/The-Constant-Gardener-film-by-Meirelles</ref>. Ubwitonzi bwa Justin ariko bwitondewe kubihingwa bye ninsanganyamatsiko yagarukaga, aho ishusho ya firime yakomotse<ref>https://dramatica.com/articles/the-constant-gardener</ref>. Hubert Koundé, Danny Huston, Bill Nighy, Pete Postlethwaite, na Donald Sumpter bakoranye<ref>http://www.filmeducation.org/pdf/film/Constant%20Gardener.pdf</ref>. Iyi filime yagenze neza kandi yinjiza amafaranga menshi kandi yegukana ibihembo bine bya Oscar, yegukana umukinnyi wa filime witwaye neza muri Rachel Weisz<ref>https://www.legendarytrips.com/trip/the-constant-gardener-filming-locations-kenya/</ref>.

